There will be only two Premier League fixtures this Sunday. The first match will see Bournemouth host Everton at the Vitality Stadium. Arsenal travel to Watford for a London Derby in the last game of the week. The Gunners have not won since the second week of the season and will be looking to push up further up the table. Sunday, September 15
